    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(…) <emph>scriptum sigillatum</emph> quod (…) continebat, qualiter domnus
                            <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/157">Paldolfus</persName> et
                            <persName ref="#people/3696" key="#Princeps">Paldolfus</persName>
                        principibus concesserat <name ref="Ligorius Atranense f. qd. Iohannis"
                            >Ligori Atrianense</name> filio quondam <name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohanni</name>
                        <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >terra vacua</rs> in ipsa ripa de intus hanc <placeName ref="#places/84"
                            key="#Cities #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >Salernitanam</placeName> pertinentem Palatio in vico sancte Trefomee a
                        super casa eius <rs key="#Confinia">per finis</rs>: ab oriente fine eius et
                            <name ref="Leo">Leoni</name> germani sui, et per ipsa fine saliente
                        usque ipsa ripa maiore: a septentrionalis fine ipsa ripa: ab occidente
                        similiter fine eius: a meridie fine <name
                            ref="Iohannes Atrianense qui dicitur Spiczacanzone">Iohanni
                            Atrianense</name> qui dicitur Spiczacanzone et de germano eius; cessante
                        a casa eorum pedes quadtuordecim, et per eadem fine exiente et coniungente
                        ad fine ipsius Ligori, per ipse finis inclitum illut ipsius Ligori
                        concesserat; (…)</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
